# Flextide Design System / Styleguide Overview

## Typography

Font family: "Inter", sans-serif (modern, legible UI font)
Headings: semi-bold, uppercase, primary blue (#3B3B4D)
Body text: regular weight, neutral dark (#121417)
Callouts / labels: medium weight, secondary teal (#3BCBB8) or primary accent (#5667FF)

## UI Elements

  - Buttons: solid primary blue background (#3B3B4D), white text, primary accent hover (#5667FF)
  - Focus indicators: glowing outline in primary accent #5667FF
  - Panels: white background with neutral border (#E2E4E9) and subtle shadow
  - Inputs: white background with medium neutral border, highlight border on focus (primary accent)
  - Icons: primary accent or secondary colors depending on state
  - Alerts: background colored according to semantic colors (success, warning, error, info) with white text

## Layout

  - Clean whitespace and consistent padding (16px base)
  - Use neutral backgrounds to reduce eye strain
  - Use semantic colors sparingly for user feedback

