## Color Variants for Node Types

| Node Type            | Color                      | Usage Description                               |
| -------------------- | -------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| Data Nodes           | #3BCBB8 (Secondary Teal)   | Indicates data-related processing nodes         |
| AI Nodes             | #7A6FF0 (Secondary Purple) | Represents AI or ML-related nodes               |
| Success States       | #1DBF73                    | Nodes or steps completing successfully          |
| Warning / Caution    | #FFB74D                    | Nodes with warnings or requiring attention      |
| Error States         | #E53935                    | Error or failed nodes                           |
| Info / Neutral State | #2196F3                    | Informational statuses or neutral process steps |